  "body": "The fork between Constantinople and Istanbul is known by two different names.  The Reference Tests refer to it as ConstantinopleFix, and hive integration tests refer to it as Petersburg.  We should allow genesis files to support both.\r\n\r\n* Either `constantinopleFixBlock` or `petersburgBlock` can be specified in a genesis file\r\n* It is an error to specify both\r\n* default .json files should migrate to `petersburgBlock`\r\n* it is not necessary to change all code occurrences of `constantinopleFix`. If done it should be in a separate single-purpose PR.",
